  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Demus writes to his wife about the wound in his head.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">Mary Jane Demus</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1863-10-17">October the 17th</date>
     </dateline>
     <salute><orig reg="My">Mi</orig> Dear</salute>
    </opener>

    <p>i take this <orig reg="opportunity">optuity</orig> to set down to let you <orig reg="know"
      >now</orig> that i have <orig reg="receive">receve</orig>
     <orig reg="your">yor</orig> letter and Was <orig reg="very">verry</orig>
     <orig reg="happy">hapey</orig> to hear from you <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i had that that you
     had <unclear>giveing</unclear>
     <orig reg="writing">righing</orig> to me <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i have <orig reg="wrote"
      >rote</orig> so much and i got no <orig reg="answer">anes</orig> till now and if you <orig
      reg="know">now</orig> how glad i Was <orig reg="When">Whean</orig> i got that <orig reg="Why"
      >Wiy</orig> you <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig>
     <orig reg="laughed">laft</orig> to <orig reg="yourself">yor self</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i had got out of <orig reg="heart">harte</orig>
     <orig reg="Waiting">Waying</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig> a letter but i am sorry <orig reg="for">fer</orig>
     <orig reg="What">Wot</orig> i <orig reg="said">sade</orig>
     <orig reg="in">i</orig> the last letter but still i <orig reg="Can't">Cant</orig> blame you
      <orig reg="for">fer</orig> not <orig reg="writing">righting</orig> if you <orig reg="Wasn't"
      >Wason</orig> at home but i must tell you <orig reg="what">whot</orig> i <orig reg="Do"
     >Dow</orig> now <orig reg="some">som</orig> days i <orig reg="fill">fil</orig> a <orig
      reg="Canteen">Cant tean</orig> and <orig reg="sometimes">som times</orig> i <orig reg="go">gow</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig>
     <unclear>orstter</unclear> and then i stay all day <orig reg="about">a bout</orig> a miles
      <orig reg="from">frum</orig>
     <orig reg="Camp">Campe</orig> and i <orig reg="ain't">ant</orig>
     <orig reg="Done">Don</orig>
     <unclear>nobe</unclear>
     <orig reg="Work">Wark</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig>
     <orig reg="about">aboute</orig> a <orig reg="month">monthe</orig> but i have got <orig
      reg="pretty">purty</orig> well <orig reg="again">a gane</orig> but i Was <orig reg="Washing"
      >Wasing</orig>
     <orig reg="my">mi</orig> head and i felt <orig reg="something">soming</orig> in the hole and i
     put <orig reg="my">mi</orig> hand <orig reg="up">oup</orig> in the hole and i <orig
      reg="pulled">pold</orig> out a <orig reg="piece">peace</orig> of <orig reg="my">mi</orig>
     <unclear>Cule</unclear> and it has got <orig reg="sore">sor</orig>
     <orig reg="again">a gane</orig> but i thing it Will get Well <orig reg="again">a gane</orig>
     but i am <orig reg="getting">geting</orig>
     <orig reg="along">a long</orig>
     <orig reg="very">verry</orig> Well at this time and i <orig reg="don't">dont</orig>
     <orig reg="know">no</orig>
     <orig reg="Whether">Wether</orig> i Will <orig reg="Come">Cum</orig> home <orig reg="soon"
     >sone</orig> or not i had <orig reg="thought">that</orig> that i <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig>
     stay till <orig reg="Christmas">Crissumous</orig> and i <orig reg="Won't">Wont</orig>
     <orig reg="make">mak</orig> it longer then <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i <orig reg="think"
     >thik</orig> that We Will be <unclear>nearder</unclear> home then it is so far that i <orig
      reg="don't">dont</orig> like to store <unclear>fest</unclear> big <orig reg="myself">mi
     selfe</orig> nothing <orig reg="more">mor</orig> give <orig reg="my">mi</orig> love to <orig
      reg="aunt">ant</orig>
     <orig reg="mary">marrey</orig> and <orig reg="uncle">unkel</orig> sol harson and all the <orig
      reg="friends">frends</orig> i had <orig reg="wrote">rote</orig> to <orig reg="Aunt">Ant</orig>
     <orig reg="Mary">Marrey</orig> but i <orig reg="haven't">hant</orig> got no
     <unclear>anles</unclear> yet i <orig reg="wrote">rote</orig> to <unclear>lysey</unclear> too
     and tell <unclear>lysey</unclear> to <orig reg="write">righte</orig> and send me a <orig
      reg="lock">lok</orig> of her head <orig reg="hair">hear</orig> and tell giney gater that <orig
      reg="her">hear</orig> Dear is <orig reg="very">verry</orig>
     <orig reg="sorry">sorrey</orig> to hear of his likenes but he say that he Will get it <orig
      reg="taken">takeing</orig>
     <orig reg="again">a gane</orig> if it Cost twenty <orig reg="Dollar">Doller</orig> and give
      <orig reg="my">mi</orig> love to ginney and <orig reg="aunt">ant</orig> marry harson that i
     think it but a <orig reg="short">sorte</orig> time since i <orig reg="left">lefte</orig> home
     nothing <orig reg="more">mor</orig> at <orig reg="Present">Presen</orig> but <orig reg="good"
      >god</orig> night</p>

    <closer>
     <salute>With a <orig reg="sweet">sweat</orig>
      <orig reg="Kiss">Cass</orig>
      <orig reg="your">yor</orig> Dear <orig reg="husband">husben</orig></salute>
     <signed>David A Demus</signed>
